**Summary:** This documentation explains how to use Amplitude's Compass chart feature to identify inflection metrics that predict user retention or conversion by analyzing base cohorts (e.g., new users) against target cohorts (e.g., retained users) using statistical measures like PPV, sensitivity, NPV, and specificity within contingency matrices.

